2014
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 6712—16S (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FF9DFFC3F9ADADE4843AFD40" box="[984,1119,650,676]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/OM720039" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">OM720039</accessionNumber>
), COI (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FF9DFFC3FEC5ADE48551FD41" box="[1200,1332,650,677]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/OM672404" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">OM672404</accessionNumber>
